OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FAn offshore firm has been fined
OL,7,F#267,000 after a worker was killed
OL,8,Fwhen he fell through a deck grate into
OL,9,Fthe North Sea.
OL,11,FEnsco Offshore UK Limited (EO UK Ltd)
OL,12,Fwas responsible for the operation of
OL,13,Fthe Valaris 121 offshore rig
OL,14,Finstallation when 50-year-old Jason
OL,15,FThomas, from Newport in south Wales,
OL,16,Fwas reported missing in January 2023.
OL,18,FAn HSE investigation concluded Mr
OL,19,FThomas had plunged into North Sea
OL,20,Fafter falling through a grate which
OL,21,Fhad not been properly secured.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FFellow workers on the rig had reported
OL,7,Fhearing a loud noise, and grating
OL,8,Foutside a door was found to have been
OL,9,Fdislodged.
OL,11,FMr Thomas' hard hat, gloves, and radio
OL,12,Fwere later found near the airlock door.
OL,14,FAn HM coastguard search was launched
OL,15,Fand called off the following day, and
OL,16,FJason's body was never recovered.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that the
OL,8,Fgrating panel had not been secured in
OL,9,Fline with the original equipment
OL,10,Fmanufacturer's specifications.
OL,12,FLater inspections had also not checked
OL,13,Fthe deployment of Hilti clips, which
OL,14,Fare used to secure gratings and stop
OL,15,Fthem coming loose.
OL,17,FThe HSE investigation further
OL,18,Fconcluded that wave action that
OL,19,Fafternoon "had applied sufficient
OL,20,Fupward force to the grating to cause
OL,21,Fthe fixings to fail and displace it."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FMr Thomas was an experienced offshore
OL,7,Fworker with around 16 years in the
OL,8,Findustry, according to HSE.
OL,10,FFollowing the incident, the company
OL,11,Freplaced all polymer grating across
OL,12,Fits fleet with galvanised steel
OL,13,Fgrating.
OL,15,FHSE principal inspector Stephen Hanson
OL,16,FHall said the incident was a "profound
OL,17,Ftragedy" which "left lasting mark on
OL,18,FJason's colleagues and his community."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FHe said: "The investigation was
OL,7,Fincredibly complex and thorough and we
OL,8,Fhope it has provided Mr Thomas'
OL,9,Fremaining family with some reassurance
OL,10,Fthat we did everything we could to
OL,11,Fsecure them justice.
OL,13,F"Grating systems must be designed,
OL,14,Finstalled and maintained so that they
OL,15,Fdo not present a risk to anyone that
OL,16,Fmay use them, particularly when used
OL,17,Fin environments where they are
OL,18,Fsusceptible to damage.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779379877
OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,F"Had the company taken relatively
OL,7,Fsimple measures to identify and
OL,8,Fcontrol the underlying risks,
OL,9,Fparticularly during the rig move, it
OL,10,Fis highly likely the incident would
OL,11,Fnever have occurred, and Jason would
OL,12,Fhave returned home."
OL,14,FEnsco Offshore UK Limited pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to breaching Section 3(1) and
OL,16,F33(1)(a) of the Health and Safety at
OL,17,FWork etc. Act 1974.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
