OL,3,CFirm fined after death of North Sea
OL,4,Cworker whose body was never recovered
OL,6,FAt Aberdeen Sheriff's Court on 18 May
OL,7,F2026, the company was fined #267,000
OL,8,Fwith an added victim surcharge of
OL,9,F#20,025 also imposed, taking the total
OL,10,Fpayable to #287,025.
